功能一样，Chore 甚至可能不会公开发布。如果真的如此，这对于以叫车和餐厅配送服务而闻名的优步来说将是一项巨大的新事业。过去几个月，Uber 在更多地点<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/uber-is-expanding-availability-of-shared-rides-and-other-green-services-122009008.html">推出了 Carshare</a> ，让用户可以从私人车主那里借车，作为到 2040 年成为零排放平台努力的一部分。它还开始<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/you-can-now-call-an-uber-like-a-normal-taxi-150006675.html?_fsig=n_cUQ3HQqPpp0rbin8_OUQ--%7EA" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/you-can-now-call-an-uber-like-a-normal-taxi-150006675.html?_fsig=n_cUQ3HQqPpp0rbin8_OUQ--%7EA">测试免费电话号码</a>1-833 -USE-UBER (1-833-873-8237) — 您可以致电安排立即或将来的行程。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/uber-could-launch-a-service-similar-to-taskrabbit-133017852.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/uber-could-launch-a-service-similar-to-taskrabbit-133017852.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> eb0766bf-5ea4-4a93-ae4c-c20e9e2211a4</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 09 Sep 2023 13:30:17 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694265183</ingested><modified> 2023-09-09T13:13:06+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Professional Services]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="2000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ab41e530-4f04-11ee-be3f-233525c950db" width="3000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></med