3n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/CheckMyAdsHQ/status/1700170006372217137"><ins>报告</ins></a>他们发现的任何示例。 </p><div id="542f950de7ba4236864702e9de172378"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们从你们那里得到了一些关于未标记为广告的 Twitter 广告的精彩示例。将这些屏幕截图以及您使用 Twitter 的方式（iOS/Android 应用程序或网络）发送至 Submit@checkmyads.org。 <a href="https://t.co/wIXsiLzCj0">pic.twitter.com/wIXsiLzCj0</a></p> — 检查我的广告 (@CheckMyAdsHQ) <a href="https://twitter.com/CheckMyAdsHQ/status/1700170006372217137?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 8 日</a></blockquote></div><p>目前尚不清楚这些未标记的广告是错误造成的还是该公司有意更改的结果。 X 不再设有正常运作的通讯部门，没有回应置评请求。</p><p>但自从埃隆·马斯克(Elon Musk)接管该公司以来，该公司的广告业务去年崩溃，这已不是什么秘密。马斯克最近表示，广告收入下降了<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1698755938541330907"><ins>60%</ins></a> ，他将这一下降归咎于激进分子。该公司最近还<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The Information;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=ba0a4cdc-cec8-416a-9e93-e11b8179129c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+Information&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbdrW01wOGw0p8WuFXAfXYzBaR9vsTVXtjAmIzXmDVSR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theinformation.com%2Fbriefings%2Fsecond-x-brand-safety-head-departs-in-months%3Frc%3Dwhf0fd" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.theinformation.com/briefings/second-x-brand-safety-head-departs-in-months?rc=whf0fd"><ins>失去了</ins></a><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/twitters-head-of-brand-safety-and-ad-quality-has-left-the-company-191401704.html"><ins>两名</ins></a>负责品牌安全的高管，广告商将这一问题视为主要担忧和退出该平台的原因。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/x-seems-to-be-slipping-unlabeled-ads-into-peoples-feeds-204234161.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/x-seems-to-be-slipping-unlabeled-ads-into-peoples-feeds-204234161.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 12fadbb5-d1b1-4d02-a03e-41cb773e4cc0</guid><dc:creator>卡丽莎·贝尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Sep 2023 20:42:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694205755</ingested><modified> 2023-09-08T20:42:39+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Karissa Bell]]></category><media:content height="3327" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ef768450-4e86-11ee-8ddd-2a3965ac3ef6" width="5000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3327" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/ef768450-4e86-11ee-8ddd-2a3965ac3ef6" width="5000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[SOPA Images via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[POLAND - 2023/07/28: n this photo illustration a New Twiiter logo (X) is displayed on a smartphone. (Photo Illustration by Omar Marques/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[n this photo illustration a New Twiiter logo (X) is...]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The AI-generated fake Drake and The Weeknd track is 'not eligible' for a Grammy]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>唱片学院首席执行官小哈维·梅森 (Harvey Mason Jr.) 正在澄清事实。 <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://variety.com/2023/music/news/ai-generated-drake-the-weeknd-song-submitted-for-grammys-1235714805/" data-original-link="https://variety.com/2023/music/news/ai-generated-drake-the-weeknd-song-submitted-for-grammys-1235714805/"><em>《Variety》</em></a>本周早些时候报道称，一首<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-grammys-will-consider-that-viral-song-with-drake-and-the-weeknd-ai-vocals-for-awards-after-all-181211888.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/the-grammys-will-consider-that-viral-song-with-drake-and-the-weeknd-ai-vocals-for-awards-after-all-181211888.html">由人工智能生成的、与 Drake 和 The Weeknd 相呼应的歌曲</a>将被考虑获得格莱美奖，之后梅森坚称事实并非如此。这首歌《 <em>Heart on My Sleeve》</em>是由化名“Ghostwriter”的人创作并提交供考虑的。这首歌的歌词由 Ghostwriter 撰写，但未经同意就模仿了说唱歌手的声音。</p><p>尽管如此，在接受<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/05/arts/music/ghostwriter-whiplash-travis-scott-21-savage.html" data-original-link="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/05/arts/music/ghostwriter-whiplash-travis-scott-21-savage.html"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时，梅森表示，从技术上讲，由于歌词，这首歌符合词曲作者类别的资格。 “就创意而言，它绝对合格，因为它是由人类编写的，”他说。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>然而，事情似乎已经发生了变化。在最近由<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://deadline.com/2023/09/ghostwriter-grammys-heart-on-my-sleeve-1235540372/" data-original-link="https://deadline.com/2023/09/ghostwriter-grammys-heart-on-my-sleeve-1235540372/"><em>Deadline</em></a>首次发现的 Instagram 帖子中，梅森给出了一些澄清。首席执行官明确表示这首歌“没有资格获得格莱美奖”。</p><p> “让我特别、特别明确的是：尽管它是由人类创作者创作的，但人声并不是合法获得的，人声也没有得到唱片公司或艺术家的许可，而且这首歌无法在商业上销售，因此，它是没有资格，”他说。 </p><div id="48fa1841be4e4a2e9070d3af00796a99"><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cw6xctbOH79/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style="background:#FFF;border:0;margin:1px;max-width:540px;min-width:326px;padding:0;width:99.375%;"><div style="padding:16px;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cw6xctbOH79/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style="background:#FFFFFF;padding:0 0;text-align:center;text-decoration:none;width:100%;" target="_blank"><div style="display:flex;"><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:40px;margin-right:14px;width:40px;"></div><div style="display:flex;"><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:14px;margin-bottom:6px;width:100px;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:14px;width:60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding:19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block;height:50px;margin:0 auto 12px;width:50px;"></div><div style="padding-top:8px;"><div style="color:#3897f0;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;">在 Instagram 上查看这篇文章</div></div><div style="padding:12.5% 0;"></div><div style="display:flex;margin-bottom:14px;"><div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:12.5px;width:12.5px;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:12.5px;width:12.5px;margin-right:14px;margin-left:2px;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:12.5px;width:12.5px;"></div></div><div style="margin-left:8px;"><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:20px;width:20px;"></div><div style="width:0;height:0;border-top:2px solid transparent;border-left:6px solid #f4f4f4;border-bottom:2px solid transparent;"></div></div><div style="margin-left:auto;"><div style="width:0px;border-top:8px solid #F4F4F4;border-right:8px solid transparent;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:12px;width:16px;"></div><div style="width:0;height:0;border-top:8px solid #F4F4F4;border-left:8px solid transparent;"></div></div></div><div style="display:flex;margin-bottom:24px;"><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:14px;margin-bottom:6px;width:224px;"></div><div style="background-color:#F4F4F4;height:14px;width:144px;"></div></div><p style="color:#c9c8cd;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:0;margin-top:8px;overflow:hidden;padding:8px 0 7px;text-align:center;white-space:nowrap;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cw6xctbOH79/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style="color:#c9c8cd;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">小哈维梅森分享的帖子。 （@harveymasonjr）</a></p></div></blockquote></div><p>根据梅森的声明，问题似乎不在于曲目是使用人工智能生成的，而是围绕同意的棘手问题。这可能意味着格莱美奖会考虑由人工智能创建的曲目，只要获得必要的许可并通过适当的渠道分发即可。但是，尽管梅森认为该行业必须发展并适应人工智能， <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/copyright-in-spotlight-after-streaming-platforms-pull-ai-generated-drake-song-183513972.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/copyright-in-spotlight-after-streaming-platforms-pull-ai-generated-drake-song-183513972.html">但版权问题仍然很复杂</a>。在代表 Drake 和 The Weeknd 的环球音乐集团提出投诉后， <em>《Heart on My Sleeve》</em>最近从 Apple Music、Spotify、Tidal 和 YouTube 等流媒体服务中下架。</p><p> “我非常认真地对待这件事，”梅森说。 “这一切都很复杂，而且进展非常非常快。我确信事情将继续发展和改变。”</p><p>至于 Ghostwriter，创作者已经发布了一首使用 AI 模仿说唱歌手 Travis Scott 和 21 Savage 的新歌。新歌《 <em>Whiplash》</em>被发布到社交媒体平台，包括 TikTok 和 X（以前称为 Twitter），而不是 Spotify 和其他流媒体服务。代笔作家还标记了请求官方合作的说唱歌手。虽然这首歌似乎在平台上引起了一些粉丝的共鸣，但 Scott 和 21 Savage 都没有做出回应。 </p><div id="89db8339b7c043769eb7e4ca8b73f02f"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">已经有一段时间了……现在无法杀死鬼魂<a href="https://twitter.com/trvisXX?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@trvisXX</a> x <a href="https://twitter.com/21savage?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@21savage</a> <a href="https://t.co/LsoisHThS5">pic.twitter.com/LsoisHThS5</a></p> - 代笔作家 (@ghostwriter977) <a href="https://twitter.com/ghostwriter977/status/1699522373861454291?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 6 日</a></blockquote></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-ai- generated-fake-drake-and-the-weeknd-track-is-not-eligible-for-a-grammy-200924948.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-ai-generated-fake-drake-and-the-weeknd-track-is-not-eligible-for-a-grammy-200924948.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 72a50169-697a-49fe-824a-0ee6aaced462</guid><dc:creator>斯蒂芬妮·巴恩斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Sep 2023 20:09:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1694439556</ingested><modified> 2023-09-11T13:39:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Stephanie Barnes]]></category><media:content height="3667" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/9c5d9dc0-4e82-11ee-bbff-1d557023dbc7" width="5500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3667" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/9c5d9dc0-4e82-11ee-bbff-1d557023dbc7" width="5500"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[REUTERS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Michael Romanowski and Charlie Post pose with the Grammy for Best Classical Engineered Album for "Bates: Philharmonia Fantastique - The Making Of The Orchestra" during the Premiere Ceremony of the 65th Annual Grammy Awards in Los Angeles, California, U.S., February 5, 2023. REUTERS/Mike Blake - HP1EJ2601R891